{"tid":490290,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"終於可以同連登班小學雞、5p仔講byebye","createTime":"2017-12-05T13:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T04:36:02.000Z","uid":3711,"like":30,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef69dfd54706b603178b436c2d31bf897bd5edf","tid":490290,"uid":3711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:12:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 忍撚夠你地班垃圾<br />\n啲五毛、新會然、假膠、打手block極都block唔晒<br />\n成班小學雞係咁係度開啲咩俾一百萬你點點點既投票post，成人台又一堆招fd子傾淫野既5p，班假膠又係咁回帶香討啲垃圾文，仲有時事台班五毛見到就火撚滾<br />\n最近仲有人搞埋啲個人簽名，差啲以為自己返咗去msn年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最撚煩就係無論乜post都實有啲搏出位既on9言論 想引人注意咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ne.g.用到爛既「好尷尬」、有女人既新聞就話「勞資糾紛」、仲有一啲懶係好有見解既冷血言論etc<br />\n唔講會員質素有幾差，淨係呢個平台已經留唔落去<br />\n一開頭以為由高登過黎可以唔洗再俾牙祖撚狗<br />\n點知過咗黎一排就見真章了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本連狗都係當我地狗咁撚 <br />\n唔講佢啲廣告有幾撚多 <br />\n淨係個垃圾收費plan已足以收皮<br />\n一早叫佢搞收費去廣告 佢就瘋狂拖時間<br />\n好喇搞喇 屌你老母每月計？<br />\n係唔係真係咁撚想賺錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"52da979821346d2b4abf28208820fff6f0650978","tid":490290,"uid":3711,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:20:45.000Z","msg":"未打完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫佢出個俾錢買永久既就唔撚理<br />\n仲要人入佢條link俾錢 連少少錢都唔想蝕俾app store<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有一直叫連狗搞pm 佢根本冇撚咗回事咁<br />\n俾唔撚起錢就焗住睇廣告 仲愈加愈多<br />\n錢就照收 意見就懶理<br />\n我就忍撚夠回家喇 <br />\n反正兩舊都係屎 唯有食舊冇咁臭既<br />\n至少高登啲會員都叫做高質啲<br />\nBye bye喇你地班垃圾低質會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ba52b44b8b93e9cfdf5aa462b7338967cc7074","tid":490290,"uid":1833,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:28:15.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n呢到冇野多<br />\n最撚多就係狗公同小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成撚都有啲狗公叫春post <br />\n咩放底tg希望有人搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab02b55b0513f61ad19c04a4b43271f74ac2d72d","tid":490290,"uid":3711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認同<br />\n呢到冇野多<br />\n最撚多就係狗公同小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成撚都有啲狗公叫春post <br />\n咩放底tg希望有人搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇見都眼怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559f1fa101b43cdd5ff7d02f0074e3336874b0b2","tid":490290,"uid":3711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:14:47.000Z","msg":"推到俾連狗睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d19a619746e989860089d85f1b8fb1563b7f4b1","tid":490290,"uid":3711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:37:54.000Z","msg":"兩隻狗公偷偷留下負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62db3ff8bc152738d253b06fd7925d23dddf7ed","tid":490290,"uid":3711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cce233d045f3dbcc4d45c5eed3a134082db4b2c","tid":490290,"uid":69064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:32:15.000Z","msg":"真的<br />\n上連登都係當上5p咁上下"},{"pid":"61b4eb20f699a8e503cbcef024479a9798e92f5b","tid":490290,"uid":37605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:00:46.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9c6e124fb5f79bcc50b18051d8c9986b99d2ae","tid":490290,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:02:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8362b033d9ec7b9a776703e9f53ea0ea287fbf5","tid":490290,"uid":53105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:04:26.000Z","msg":"唔送啦，希望你